{"tid":1003143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跨境學童衣服縫夾藏口袋 走私165部手機","createTime":"2019-01-31T12:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T08:28:07.000Z","uid":70063,"like":7,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7f56acbcf9bfb5e6208b62d26ea32a8f39f0c8","tid":1003143,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:13:36.000Z","msg":"深圳海關上周三在5名跨境學童身上查獲165部手提電話及一批化妝品。<br />\n<br />\n警方指學童年齡介乎8至13歲，他們的衣服縫有夾藏口袋，用作收藏貨物。<br />\n<br />\n海關關員立即聯絡家長到場協助調查，但家長均沒有出現。關員最後只能委托當地派出所，聯絡家長接走學童。<br />\n<br />\n海關強調利用學童走私，作為監護人須承擔相應法律責任，案件仍在進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2021486531329156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fposts%2F2021486531329156&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=8f9fb2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2021486531329156</a>"},{"pid":"7a93684dd396659cb231719a012802fa1d150587","tid":1003143,"uid":45603,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"細路仔都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 壓撚矮哂佢地就啱架啦"},{"pid":"2e2d4d4d729e4d5f632e5cfc47e1d63bcd3249a8","tid":1003143,"uid":82940,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"海關關員立即聯絡家長到場協助調查，但家長均沒有出現。關員最後只能委托當地派出所，聯絡家長接走學童。<br />\n<br />\n完 走鳩晒"},{"pid":"340a25ec8d8eb7eea9da794c430a3bd0046fa707","tid":1003143,"uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"本性難移<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a8130ea6876b69df711c9dba6d87b9e216528a","tid":1003143,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:50:40.000Z","msg":"五個小朋友點收埋165部手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a32b06ea44d1bea97c4ae802090d6ca541b4be","tid":1003143,"uid":36178,"like":0,"disli